br />\n如果本身你鐘意穩穩陣陣，又唔太留意新聞同細心思考<br />\n我建議你都係唔好諗咁多，不如買舊實金放屋企算<br />\n唔好太多幻想見到師奶變富婆，呢個世界冇咁多好彩<br />\n就算係玩財技嘅大鱷都未必預計到下一個部署會衍生到啲咩新驚喜<br />\n<br />\n如果你有冒險精神，覺得金錢只不過係數字遊戲。<br />\n就唔好冇錢嗰陣怨天怨地怨消息，要學識主導/跟隨大勢嘅動力<br />\n<br />\n純9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為我已經玩到傻咗"},{"pid":"d77bf9bcf6daeb29a2175361446ec99626b708ec","tid":2008143,"uid":255333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:41:53.000Z","msg":"呢本當入門工具書OK，正價$150有500幾頁基本嘢算整<br />\n<br />\n雖然睇完你會覺得好似識咗好多嘢，不過其實未夠用，仲要加埋實戰觀察同互動去領略各種工具嘅應用(幾時work幾時唔work)，不過有心嘅話就行第一步學咗先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VM8JEVg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVM8JEVg.png&h=887c9113&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80ba31d32851304e7d81fd200cd14d3e024abc14","tid":2008143,"uid":293355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3f512a7bb40b47b13e5e6b8c51e80b818e5a00f","tid":2008143,"uid":165102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T21:53:21.000Z","msg":"之前一直都淨係抽新股去賺錢<br />\n自知自己無底所以唔敢亂黎<br />\n想認真學翻d技術面嘅嘢先炒股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下各位巴打<br />\n有冇咩理論應該要學左先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家睇緊Youtube 學 唔知有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1994922/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1994922/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n技術分析睇呢個po啦, 純圖表派師兄教, 想知多D我再答"},{"pid":"d4a58a1c6d4e84529e581705b6ef81de53389f4f","tid":2008143,"uid":317577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b5a09b42638f66ddc1c7d3c678c5c1f43004df3","tid":2008143,"uid":7206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"c